data.description: Well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath Cape with 1 car garage in a great location. As you enter through the enclosed front porch and foyer, you'll be welcomed into the large, fireplaced living room with it's hardwood floors & built-ins. Beyond the living room you'll step into the dining room with large bay window. Next, the eat-in kitchen has special features such as a breakfast nook, pantry storage, laundry room and built in ironing board. Opposite the kitchen is a separate room that can serve as formal space or a home office. A bedroom and one full bath finish off the main level. Upstairs you'll find 2 more large bedrooms, a cedar closet and walk in attic access. On the lower level there is a second laundry hookup, another full bath with shower stall as well as a partially finished area with decorative, non-working fireplace that adds to the decor. Outside features include a detached one car garage, a large trex deck, a patio area and the private, fully fenced backyard. Conveniently located close to all West Hartford has to offer. Dining, shopping, major highways, entertainment and so much more.
